      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ONEDARKNIGHT NZ (8) has had two runs this prep and is yet to finish in the top three. Added to the sequence last time over 1730m at Bathurst, finishing 16 metres away from the winner in ninth. Drawn to enjoy a cosy run but might need things to go his way at some stage. Good enough to take out a race like this. BOY STUNNER (2) has been racing well of late. Finished second at his latest appearance over 1770m at this track, beaten 8 metres. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Meets a comparable field and he can figure in the finish. FLY OVER STATES (1) has been thereabouts of late and is a great chance to break through. Good effort last time out when he finished fifth at this track over 1770m. ARMA THE GREAT (7) is the best of the rest after finishing third when resuming over 1770m at this track last time out.",
